= class GLib::ConverterOutputStream

GLib::ConverterOutputStream implements GLib::OutputStream and allows conversion
of data of various types during writing.

== Object Hierarchy

* Object
  * GLib::Instantiatable
    * GLib::Object
      * GLib::OutputStream
        * GLib::FilterOutputStream
          * GLib::ConverterOutputStream

== Class Methods

--- GLib::ConverterOutputStream.new(base_stream, converter)

     Creates a new GLib::ConverterOutputStream for ((|base_stream|)), using
     ((|converter|)) for conversions.

     * base_stream: A Glib::OutputStream
     * converter: A GLib::Converter
     * Returns: a new GLib::ConverterOutputStream

== Instance Methods

--- converter

     Gets the GLib::Converter that is used for conversions.

     * Returns: The GLib::Converter that is used for conversions

== Properties

--- converter: GLib::Converter (Read/Write)

     The GLib::Converter that is used for conversions

